        "备注": "PVC证卡工作证定制【统一内容的/单独人像需要单独收费】",
        "完整描述": "In today's fast-paced world, businesses, schools, and events need reliable identification solutions that are both functional and customizable. That's where our pvc card customization service comes in. Whether you need employee id badges, school hall passes, event credentials, or access cards, our durable pvc cards offer the perfect solution. Measuring 3.39x2.13 inches, these cards are fully customizable in size, content, and design. We can print high-resolution images, text, and even integrate access control features for secure entry. The accompanying lanyards can also be tailored to match your brand. From corporate offices to school campuses, our pvc cards ensure seamless identification and security. They're a versatile tool that enhances organization and boosts professionalism.",
